  "body": "### Component\r\n\r\nForge\r\n\r\n### Describe the feature you would like\r\n\r\nforge snapshot can be a bit pedantic:\r\n\r\nhttps://twitter.com/devtooligan/status/1551965598149513216\r\n\r\n<img width=\"594\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/19890894/181060852-ec005a0b-7cda-490e-b596-8aac36032169.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\nthere was some discussion re merging --gas-report and snapshot https://github.com/foundry-rs/foundry/issues/2065#issuecomment-1163136664 but given that both serve different purposes it wasn't merged yet.\r\n\r\nforge snapshot has been neglected a bit #2056\r\n\r\nadding thresholds and name filters would be a quick fix though\r\n\r\nthis also should be configurable via config, see #2509\r\n\r\n### Additional context\r\n\r\n_No response_",
